Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.37,0:01:33.95,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1481,472)}Episode 9: Attack of the Ogres
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.54,0:01:35.41,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Rimuru and the Goblins' development of \Ntheir village continued to progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:40.95,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Kaijin and the three Dwarf brothers, \NGarm, Dord, and Myrd,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:44.59,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,made clothing and tools and built more homes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:49.43,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,while the Goblin Lords under Rigurd worked \Nout a system for ruling the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:53.13,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's going great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:56.75,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Even without my orders, \Neveryone's doing their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:58.49,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Makes it easier for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.76,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's something \Nimportant I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.53,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Good. No one's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There, all fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:22.29,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Shizu-san, I'll take good \Ncare of this keepsake of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.34,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:38.85,sign_3737_16_Mimic____Human,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,516)}Mimic => Human
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:42.79,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This Mimic works really smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:45.23,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,An actual human body... \NFeels great to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:49.90,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.33,0:02:52.20,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:02.95,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I think I could see and \Nhear things better as a slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.67,0:03:05.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Magic Sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.59,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So, next...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.23,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Great Sage, since I ate Ifrit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,can I use body doubles now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:14.89,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.51,sign_4961_43_It_hurts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(482,637)}Analysis Complete
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:19.81,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,All of Ifrit's skills, including \NBody Double, have been analyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:19.81,sign_4748_29_All_of_Ifrit_s_s,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1063,1)}\h\hAll of Ifrit's skills,\h\h\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hincluding\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\N\h\h\h\h\h\hBody Double,\h\h\h\h\h\N\hhave been analyzed.\h
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:21.22,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.68,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try it out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:25.40,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Body Double!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:29.90,sign_3737_16_Mimic____Human,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(525,515)}Body Double
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.67,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I see... It does look like Shizu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,No trace at all of how I \Nlooked when I was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:42.53,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What a beautiful... boy? Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:48.75,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I need to know what sex my \Nbody is when in human form, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:53.09,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Though I can kind of already tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:57.05,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But since I didn't actually \Ncheck to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:03.64,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,My son didn't make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:07.21,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I seem rather androgynous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:09.40,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I have no gender at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.15,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sexless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:16.91,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I had no \Ngender as a slime, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:19.46,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:23.41,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,when I took human form earlier, \NI didn't see any black mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.77,0:04:24.42,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:24.42,sign_6326_48_Answer,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(527,1)}Answer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:28.02,sign_6326_48_Answer,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,When using Mimic to assume a \Nform larger than one's own,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:31.67,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,black mist produced by magicule \Nconsumption makes up the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:31.67,sign_6453_51_Black__Mist,,0000,0000,0000,,Black \NMist
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:36.61,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Which means... I could \Ncreate an adult form, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:37.57,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh! Can I make it look masculine?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.24,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's pretty handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:55.17,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now make it feminine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:04:59.93,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:03.37,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, stop! Stop! Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.69,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that. \NGiving myself an adult female form
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.69,0:05:12.46,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,makes me look like Shizu-san, \Nand that just feels immoral.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.22,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,That concludes my report.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.86,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, no problems. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.41,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.48,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you will \Nneed no food again today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:29.45,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't taste anything \Nas a slime anywa—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.48,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Rigurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.48,0:05:34.25,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:37.05,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat with you guys starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.07,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Truly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.49,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Then we must prepare a lavish feast tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:43.84,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:44.50,Main,Rigurd,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:50.94,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Since I can \Nmimic a human form now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:53.22,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat all kinds of tasty food!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:56.95,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's on the menu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:59.26,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Meat, maybe? There'll probably be meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:01.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I'll want rice, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:03.75,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have rice plants in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.30,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to look for some eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.02,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,If I find any, I'll make some rice fields...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.57,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:13.52,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for always getting our food for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.44,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:17.49,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,We're just on our way out to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:21.66,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a feast tonight, \Nso bring back some tasty prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.09,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to eat with us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.36,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.29,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This body has a sense of taste, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.69,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,If you eat a lot, I wonder if \Nyour boobs will get bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:41.42,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'll make sure \NGobta is strictly disciplined!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.51,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I will prepare some \Ngrade-A bulldeer for the feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:49.52,sign_9748_92_Bulldeer,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(690,1)}Bulldeer
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:51.24,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.52,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:56.13,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,Many magical beasts have been traveling \Nthis way from deep in the forest, lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.57,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,so prey is abundant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.32,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:05.17,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,No, magical beasts move from place \Nto place as the environment changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.33,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's anything serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:15.84,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,You called, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:19.36,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Ranga, go into the forest with Rigur's team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.85,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt anything will happen, \Nbut just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.14,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:29.14,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,No need for reservation, Rigur. \NTake me along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.14,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was pretty cool, Ranga!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.52,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Even cooler if you weren't doing that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:41.41,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I paid a visit to the cave \Nwhere Veldora had been sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:46.53,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to test out Degenerate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:49.39,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,the unique skill I'd received from Shizu-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.31,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,in a place where it wouldn't disturb anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:59.33,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of the impression \Ngiven by the name "Degenerate,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.60,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,the skill was important to her, \Nand that makes it precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.05,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.30,sign_11607_114_Degenerate,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1321,1)}Degenerate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:08.51,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,uses unification and separation \Nto merge skills together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.65,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,evolving them into new skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:14.14,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she used it \Nto gain a bunch of new skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.65,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,One of them was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.44,0:08:21.50,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:25.36,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,This is the extra skill, Black Flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.36,sign_3737_16_Mimic____Human,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1)}— Black Flame —
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:28.87,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to be careful \Nhow I use this one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.89,0:08:36.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.13,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I should really be grateful to Shizu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:45.51,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This mask has the power \Nto suppress magic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:47.14,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.39,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.18,sign_6326_48_Answer,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.25,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Answer.
