Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:54.30,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,The faint aura you were emitting \Nhas been completely erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:58.19,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,In this state, you would \Nbe perceived as a human.
