Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:02.44,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I should wear this \Nwhen I go to new places.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:06.73,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Lookin' good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:07.66,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
