Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.22,Italics,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:15.08,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Receiving Thought Communication from: Ranga.
