Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.47,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die! I'm dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:28.79,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.66,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,I got cut! It hurts so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.18,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. It's not deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:37.14,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:39.29,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Rimuru-sama, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:41.91,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,You got worried and came to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.27,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You seem fine, so I guess \Nyou don't need any potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.94,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I want some!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:51.16,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I joked around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.87,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That helped a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.02,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Ranga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.58,0:10:20.63,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Master, forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:22.61,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,This happened while I was here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.79,0:10:27.82,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Rigur!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.57,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,G-Rimuru-sama... I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.62,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Leave this \Nto me and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:38.71,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.59,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Ranga, what happened to \Nthe ones who've fallen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:46.88,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,They've been put to sleep with magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:49.47,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,That pink-haired one did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.49,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Magic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.37,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like these guys are gonna be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:04.20,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,How humiliating. I never thought \Nwe would run into Ogres.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.23,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Ogres?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:08.88,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The ones in games and \Nmovies look like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.95,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But these don't look like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.56,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They even have armor on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.09,0:11:19.96,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Also, those look like \NJapanese swords to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.25,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Six Ogres...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.54,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:28.21,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened, \Nbut sorry about what my guys did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.59,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be willing to talk this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:36.04,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,They're clearly much stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:38.97,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,but Gobta and Rigur weren't fatally wounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.97,0:11:42.21,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and most of our security force was \Njust put to sleep, not injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.57,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.57,0:11:47.41,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll just have to be \Nthe adult in the room and—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.26,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Show us who you really are, evil majin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:50.90,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:54.14,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang on! What did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:58.74,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Enslaving monsters is not a feat \Njust any human can accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.03,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:04.33,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,You may hide your appearance and \Nsuppress your aura, but it won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.00,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,Reveal your true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:10.01,Main,Soei,0000,0000,0000,,For the mastermind to approach \Nus himself is most convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:11.89,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:16.23,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But my true identity is \Njust a lovable slime...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.49,0:12:19.22,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:23.18,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,We have no intention of listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.48,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,That mask tells us everything \Nwe need to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.32,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,My mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:30.25,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Aren't you \Nmaking some kind of mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.25,0:12:32.21,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a keepsake of—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:36.45,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,If it will serve to repay even \Na billionth of what was done
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:38.49,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,to our brethren, we will have your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:41.20,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,You friend of those evil pigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.41,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:44.75,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Do? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:48.25,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of the pink-haired one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.00,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.42,0:12:51.10,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And don't kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:51.76,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:54.60,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's more to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.77,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Just get in their way a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:58.18,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take out the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:02.78,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,But that would mean you'd \Nbe taking on five Ogres...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.69,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.58,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,That's my master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:09.48,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.57,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.16,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you truly brave or just foolhardy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.16,0:13:18.90,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Out of respect for your sheer nerve, \NI'll go along with your provocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.49,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you don't regret it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:33.33,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You can just take a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.96,0:13:36.97,sign_3737_16_Mimic____Human,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(530,1)}— Paralysis Breath —
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.64,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I saw you with Magic Sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.71,0:13:46.64,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:49.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's not what I meant by "I saw you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:50.61,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:57.44,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're about to fall, miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:57.65,sign_20032_241_Sticky_Steel_Thr,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(521,1)}Sticky Steel Thread
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.11,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.83,sign_3737_16_Mimic____Human,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(521,1)}— Body Armor —
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.46,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.97,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,He beat us that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.13,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,So, that just leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:20.83,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What'll it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.43,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,The Evil Centipede's Paralysis Breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:29.00,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Spider's Sticky Steel Thread...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.69,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,The Armorsaurus's Body Armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:37.60,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,He may have learned the skills \Nof many other monsters, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.70,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,Do not lower your guard, young master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:43.37,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,He named all the skills I used,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.42,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and the monsters they came \Nfrom, from just one look...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:49.66,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I should try not to give too much away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.19,0:14:51.86,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:54.50,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to hear what I have to say now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.26,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, evil majin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.51,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, um... So, listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.69,0:15:01.79,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,I admit you are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.79,0:15:04.02,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me all the more certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.01,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Certain of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.52,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,You are one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:09.48,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Them? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:14.98,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,It is unthinkable for us Ogres \Nto be defeated by mere Orcs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.13,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Orc?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:18.11,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on, what makes you—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:18.98,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.98,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,I know it was all the work of \Nyou and your majin comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.53,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Majin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.37,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't deny it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.49,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You've got the wrong—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.61,0:15:36.06,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,I must be going senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.59,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,I was certain I cut off your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:40.49,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Are they serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.11,Main,Rigur,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:43.43,Main,Gobta,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.43,Main,Ranga,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:48.19,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! Don't let your guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.41,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Did he get under my Magic Sense
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:54.94,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,and easily break through my \NMultilayer Barrier and Body Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.56,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I won't miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.69,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you were just foolhardy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:04.80,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,I commend your courage to remain \Ncalm after losing an arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:12.12,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,The pride that compelled you to take \Nus all on alone will be your downfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:14.62,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Regret your folly in the next life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.47,sign_3737_16_Mimic____Human,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,1)}— Ultraspeed Regeneration —
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:33.77,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think you'd beaten me just \Nby cutting off one of my arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:36.52,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,F-Foul beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:39.32,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ogre Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:47.52,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,Young master...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.74,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Did I... get him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:57.74,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.70,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Fire has no effect on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:02.50,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,You were right, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.80,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I did underestimate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.26,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.55,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,what I'm like when I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:15.89,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,What an aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.29,0:17:18.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:29.16,sign_3737_16_Mimic____Human,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(524,1)}— Black Flame —
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.41,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's... That flame is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.78,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,It's not produced by using \Nthe surrounding magicules!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:40.92,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing forming that \Nflame is his pure strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:45.80,Main,Shura,0000,0000,0000,,And the size of the flame mirrors \Nthe size of his power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:49.55,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something \Neven more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:52.62,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,This is my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:03.86,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:08.77,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should've kept this \None under wraps, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.45,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,What now? Still want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.74,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Good, he's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:17.46,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Please just surrender now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:20.28,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,Young master, please take \Nthe princess and flee.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:21.52,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,I will end this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.34,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:27.41,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,That is intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:31.38,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,It saddens me to say it, but it \Nseems we are no match for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:38.90,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I have my pride as the next \Nleader of the powerful Ogre clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.32,0:18:43.77,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,And what leader would fail to \Navenge his slain brethren?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:48.33,Main,Benumaru,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't win, I will still fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:52.16,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,Young master, if you fight, \NI will fight by your side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:54.50,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's their answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:57.63,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, damn. That backfired on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.82,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:04.25,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,This individual may not be our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:05.45,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:06.55,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:08.80,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:13.01,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,He's a masked majin, just like \Nthe one who attacked our village!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.39,0:19:14.80,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,You said so yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:19.82,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... but please, try to \Nthink this through calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:23.56,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why would such a powerful majin \Nuse such underhanded tactics
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.53,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,as forcing the pigs to attack our village?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:27.82,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,It makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:32.32,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,He surely has the power to kill us \Nall on his own, if he so desired!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:36.08,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,There is no doubt he is unlike us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:40.57,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think he has any connection \Nto the ones that attacked our village.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.96,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling a little more willing to listen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.47,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need this anymore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.69,0:19:58.08,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:19:59.71,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:01.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:03.90,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,A slime?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Rimuru the slime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.74,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:19.20,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And this mask is a keepsake \Nfrom someone I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:22.15,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to see for yourself \Nwhether it's the same one
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.07,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,that your attacker had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.15,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.99,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,It does seem similar, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:35.30,Main,Shuna,0000,0000,0000,,This one contains anti-magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:40.48,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,But the majin from back then \Nwasn't concealing their aura...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:41.73,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:45.01,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:48.59,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,It seems our desperation caused \Na grave misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.68,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept my apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.65,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:55.79,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.79,0:20:58.31,Italics,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,For a minute there, I wasn't \Nsure what was gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.82,0:21:01.92,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is no place to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.89,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head back to the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.41,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.42,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:08.41,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:10.42,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,I want to hear about what \Nyou've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:14.80,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,But we wounded your companions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.70,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,And we did the same to yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:20.31,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,But no one died, so we'll say it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.54,0:21:22.46,Main,Hakuro,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:26.76,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we're having a feast today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,The more, the merrier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.55,0:21:36.45,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the battle that began before \Nanyone even knew why had ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:40.34,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,The Ogre princess reversed the sleep spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:42.15,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and the Goblins awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.96,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,Rimuru healed the Ogres' \Nwounds with his potion,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:49.63,Italics,Na,0000,0000,0000,,and the whole gang headed for \NRimuru and the Goblins' village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.96,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what's your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:56.42,Main,Benimaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we have no names.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.42,0:21:58.97,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I forgot, most of you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.18,0:22:01.17,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.30,0:22:03.94,Main,Rimuru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:38.72,Italics_Top,Great Sage,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "The Orc Lord."
